author: fabozzi
body:
Adding new MC relvals for BPH group.
They use new gen fragments deployed in 8_1_0_pre9.

These are the filter efficiency as provided by BPH group:
BdToMuMu: ~0.0015
BsTo MuMu: ~0.00044
BuToJpsiK: ~0.00058
BsToJpsiPhi: ~0.000116.

These new relvals have been produced for the first time in 8_1_0_pre9:
https://cms-project-relval.web.cern.ch/cms-project-relval/relval_stats/2016_07_29_2_0.txt
title: new BPH MC relvals
